	<titles>
		<title type="short" as="introduced">Conquer Childhood Cancer Act of 2007</title>
		<title type="short" as="reported to house">Caroline Pryce Walker Conquer Childhood Cancer Act of 2008</title>
		<title type="short" as="passed house">Caroline Pryce Walker Conquer Childhood Cancer Act of 2008</title>
		<title type="short" as="passed senate">Caroline Pryce Walker Conquer Childhood Cancer Act of 2008</title>
		<title type="short" as="enacted">Caroline Pryce Walker Conquer Childhood Cancer Act of 2008</title>
		<title type="official" as="introduced">To amend the Public Health Service Act to advance medical research and treatments into pediatric cancers, ensure patients and families have access to the current treatments and information regarding pediatric cancers, establish a population-based national childhood cancer database, and promote public awareness of pediatric cancers.</title>
		<title type="official" as="amended by house">To amend the Public Health Service Act to advance medical research and treatments into pediatric cancers, ensure patients and families have access to information regarding pediatric cancers and current treatments for such cancers, establish a national childhood cancer registry, and promote public awareness of pediatric cancer.</title>
